definition: few/less/to lack/to be missing/to stop (doing sth)/seldom

sentences.english: Wants efficient changeovers between products with minimum downtime.
sentences.chinese: 用最少時間進行產品間轉換。

sentences.english: A software company might give bonuses to programmers who create the fewest bugs .
sentences.chinese: 一個軟件公司可以加發獎勵給寫出最少臭蟲的程序員。

sentences.english: The 435 members of the House are elected every two years.
sentences.chinese: 最少每五年舉行一次普選來選舉下議院議員。

sentences.english: Tinned food is the least wasted.
sentences.chinese: 罐頭食品則是浪費最少的。

sentences.english: The page where the link is placed on must be minimum PR4 or above.
sentences.chinese: 所在的鏈接放在最少要有個PR4以上的頁面。

sentences.english: The labeler shall operate with a minimum of operator involvement.
sentences.chinese: 貼標籤機應當在最少的操作員介入條件下運行。

sentences.english: Formally the house seeks to be a solid with the least possible subtractions.
sentences.chinese: 形式上別墅力圖成爲一個削減最少的立方體。

sentences.english: The Hohxil Region of Qinghai Province is one of the region studied less in the world.
sentences.chinese: 青海可可西里地區是世界上最少研究的地區之一。

sentences.english: The city of foreign stock is filled with rate is very low, least only severalfold.
sentences.chinese: 國外股票的市盈率很低，最少的只有幾倍。

sentences.english: The count of microvessel was the fewest in genistein group.
sentences.chinese: 各組微血管記數結果金雀黃素組最少。

sentences.english: Booking are needed to be made at least 3days in advance.
sentences.chinese: 租埸需於最少三個工作天前預約。

sentences.english: In a game of cricket, what is the minimum number of referee(s) needed?
sentences.chinese: 在板球運動比賽中，最少需要多少名球證？

sentences.english: Among these four islands, there can be no doubt that South Island is the least polluted and most spectacularly scenic of them all.
sentences.chinese: 四個島中，南島無疑是污染最少且風景最秀麗的。

sentences.english: A sufficient number of international reply coupons (at least five).
sentences.chinese: 是說最少五張回郵券麼？

sentences.english: Of all the economically important plants，palms have been the least studied.
sentences.chinese: 在所有的經濟作物中，棕櫚樹得到的研究最少。
